Revision history for Perl extension POD2::IT.

Legenda:
   + = new feature
   ! = updated feature/bug fix
   * = incompatible changes
   - = removed feature

0.13 2009/08/25 20:00:00 
	+ Added perlreftut.pod [larsen, polettix, bepi]
	! Fixes to perlfunc.pod, perlfaq2, perlfaq6 and perlfaq9 [dree]

0.12 Mon Aug 18 00:00:00 2008
