0.07  Mon Aug 01 12:00:00 2005  
	! Updated perlboot.pod to 5.8.7 [osfameron]
	! Updated perlfunc.pod to 5.8.7 [dree]
	! Updated perlfaq[1..9] to 5.8.7 [dree]
	! Updated perlrequick to 5.8.7 [dree]
